About Cacophonic

Icon Collective grad, i have about 5 years experience tutoring mentees in music. Cacophonic's music is a fusion of trap and dubstep with hints of influence from all genres of EDM. His remixes have been featured on BBC, Radio 1, & UMF Radio, and have been played by some of the biggest names in the industry, including Diplo, Dj Snake, Afrojack, & David Guetta. Hudson began performing shows soon after his first remix was released, reaching over 100k streams in just 3 weeks, currently standing at over 2 million streams and 20k likes. His remixes have hit major festivals all over the world, including Tomorrowland MainStage, Ultra Europe, Amsterdam Music Festival and EDC Las Vegas as he has shared the stage alongside notable artists such as Of the Trees, Modestep, Peekaboo, and more. His most recent release, “Toy Lazer,” was featured on a compilation album alongside names like Ruvlo and Joki, garnering high praise from both fans and industry professionals.
